       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI77701.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI77701.
      *
      *      Manutençăo de Contas Bancárias
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
