                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO COCV7771-XDESCISTATUS7
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV7771-XDESCISTATUS8 EQUAL SPACES
