              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO COCV7771-XDESCISTATUS8
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV7771-XDESCNIDPROJECTO1 EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-NIDPROJECTO
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO1
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
                 THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
